WEBVTT

00:07.311 --> 00:07.791
You love me.

00:10.288 --> 00:10.735
You love me...

00:11.730 --> 00:12.357
...because I'm Kobe...

00:14.531 --> 00:15.765
...because I'm a five-time champion...

00:18.347 --> 00:20.127
...because I'm one of the greatest to step on the court...

00:23.849 --> 00:24.358
...but you shouldn't.

00:26.935 --> 00:27.613
You should hate me.

00:30.178 --> 00:30.476
Hate me...

00:31.551 --> 00:32.956
...because I gave you 4 AM...

00:34.781 --> 00:37.403
...because I pushed you when no one else would.

00:39.189 --> 00:42.241
Hate me because I demanded greatness.

00:44.177 --> 00:46.115
Greatness demands everything.

00:51.764 --> 00:52.052
Love me...

00:53.787 --> 00:54.730
...when you become greater.

